title: Rewterz Threat Alert EnemyBot Active IOCs

sentences: Enemybot is a new and emerging botnet that has been targeting router vulnerabilities to infect devices. The botnet resembles and borrows source codes from Mirai Botnet and Gafgyt_tQor. Enemybot also connects to CnC servers hosted on the Tor network, which makes its takedown more complicated. The malware first infects multiple environments to infect further devices. Enemybot also targets desktop/server architectures such as x64, including Darwin (macOS), and BSD.
